**Current @plcl-ui Components**:
- `Shell.tsx` - Main component with desktop/app/page/sidebar/web/window variants
- `Window.tsx` - Draggable/resizable window component
- `WindowManager.tsx` - Multi-window management
- `Settings.tsx` - Appearance settings (theme, wallpaper, icons, dock, layout)
- `Search.tsx` - App search overlay
- `Desktop.tsx` - Desktop container (internal)
- `Wallpaper.tsx` - Desktop background (internal)
- `Apps.tsx` - Desktop icons (internal)
- `IFrameApp.tsx` - Iframe wrapper for web apps

**Custom Apps Support**:
- âœ… Users can add custom apps via `customApps` prop on Shell's desktop variant
- âœ… Apps defined with `AppDefinition` interface from `@plcl/ui-types`
- âœ… Apps appear in dock, search, and desktop automatically

